metadata.name: Against All Odds
metadata.description:
What if our story is about to begin?
We weren't looking for each other
Yet here we are, 
Pulling against the stream.
Same tide, different waves,
Slow seconds of blissful waiting,
Dreams that merged into a world for two,
Stuck between horizons and tomorrows
Each one wanting to arrive 
Even earlier than today.
If forever can be ours
And now is our home,
Will you choose to stay?

Visual art, poetry, music and narration by REBELLICCA
